description:
Play as characters chosen by the Conton City Vote! Goku (Ultra Instinct -Sign-), Dyspo, and Vegeta (GT) are available in addition to new extra missions, new costumes, illustrations chosen by the Conton City Vote, and much more! 

・3 New Characters: Goku (Ultra Instinct -Sign-), Dyspo, Vegeta (GT)
・2 Extra Missions
・4 New Parallel Quests
・10 Additional Moves
・4 Costumes/Accessories
・5 Super Souls
・15 Illustrations
name: DRAGON BALL XENOVERSE 2 - Conton City Vote Pack
